I think you ought to do the logging in `getStaticPaths`, to make sure that all paths return - something like this:

```ts
export const getStaticPaths = async () => {
    const response = await client.getEntries();

    console.log(JSON.stringify(response.items, null, 2));
    
    const paths = response.items
        .filter((item) => Boolean(item?.fields?.slug))
        .map((item) => {
            return {
                params: {slug: item.fields.slug || null},
            };
        });

    return {
        paths,
        fallback: false,
    };
};
```

